text: Ramme may refer to: * Ramme (river), a river in Lower Saxony, Germany ==People with the surname== * Ernest Ramme (1916-2004), United Staes Air Force General * Jens Ramme (born 1963), German former footballer * Walter Ramme (1895-date of death unknown), German freestyle swimmer who competed in the 1912 Summer Olympics * Willy Adolf Theodor Ramme (1887–1953), German entomologist ==See also== * Ramme Gaard, an organic farm and country estate, located just north of Hvitsten in Akershus municipality, on the coast of Norway
title: Ramme
